name: EVANGELION
description: A must have for every fan! Evangelion is now on LINE! “EVANGELION:3.0” will be released in Japan on 17/11/2012! Don’t miss it!

name: K-ON!
description: The K-ON! anime is celebrating its 5th anniversary, and now the princesses of afterschool rock are rolling onto LINE. Amp up your chats with Yui and the gang!

name: FULLMETAL ALCHEMIST:BROTHERHOOD
description: Fullmetal Alchemist is here in this new sticker set! Ed, Al, and all the rest of the cast are here!

name: BAKEMONOGATARI
description: NisiOisiN brings his popular anime Bakemonogatari to LINE stickers! Koyomi Araragi and all the heroines are here to bring energy to your chats!

name: Hatsune Miku senbonsakura
description: Enjoy the super cute style of these stickers based on the world of Kuro Usapi, producer of the hit song "senbonsakura."

name: Anohana -The Flower We Saw That Day-
description: Menma, Jintan, Anaru and the other 3 super peace busters have crashed the party at LINE! Take a look at these illustrations and tell me you can't see that they're by director Tatsuyuki Nagai and character designer Masayoshi Tanaka!

name: Assassination Classroom
description: The assassination classroom pupils slink onto animated stickers. Koro-sensei, Nagisa, Karma, and your other favorite students are waiting for you to show them their true potential!

name: NISEMONOGATARI
description: NisiOishiN brings you more stickers from the second entry in his popular Monogatari anime series, Nisemonogatari. Oshinoshinobu and all your favorite characters are here to light up your chats!

name: DURARARA!!
description: The seedy underbelly of Ikebukuro comes to life in these Durarara LINE stickers! The series' colorful cast of characters are here to turn your chats into a wild night of parties and street fights.

name: STEINS;GATE
description: Wahahaha! The mad scientist Kyōma Hōōin has come to bring chaos to LINE with some craaazy stickers! Pick these stickers to go out of this world!

name: Moving ONE PIECE Commemorative Stickers
description: ONE PIECE stickers are here with Straw Hat Pirates crew favorites Ace, Sabo, Law and more in full motion!

name: NISEKOI:
description: You thought gang warfare was tough? Just wait until you step inside the topsy-turvy love triangle (and sometimes rectangle?) that is "Nisekoi." These stickers are 100% infused with laughter and confusion!

name: Monthly Girls' Nozaki-kun
description: Get ready to swoon, because here comes a set of stickers from the hit anime everybody's talking about, "Monthly Girls' Nozaki-kun!" These stickers are so easy to use you may have just accidently sent one right now! Download the set and join in this harem of hilarity.

name: YURU-YURI
description: The surprisingly normal everyday world of Yuru-Yuri just landed on LINE! This set features slightly off-kilter yet impeccably cute girls saying all sorts of things that you only wish you could! Send them to your friends to make them chortle in delight.

name: NORAGAMI
description: Yato and the rest of the gang have been caught up in a plot of divine proportions! Fortunately, this turn of events has landed them their very own LINE stickers and televised anime series "Noragami ARAGOTO!" Like, oh my gods?

name: Magi: The Labyrinth of Magic Vol. 2
description: Aladdin's back for another round of magical adventures in this dynamic new sticker set! He and all his friends are back again to dive through dungeons and claim lost treasure in this set of 40 emotive stickers.

name: Tengen Toppa Gurren Lagann
description: Kamina and his teammates in first part of Tengen Toppa Gurren Lagannepisodes come into stump!Express your hot feeling to your friends with these stumps!

name: ReLIFE
description: Serialized in the "comico"!

name: honobono log sticker
description: It is a LINE sticker appearance at last from "honobono log"! May the feeling which is not transmitted only in written form is also transmitted perfectly!

name: MY HERO ACADEMIA
description: "MY HERO ACADEMIA"which is serializing on Weekly Jump becomes sticker!You can use sticker including an intriguing Heroes and Villain!!

name: SHIROBAKO vol.1
description: TV Anime "SHIROBAKO" stickers are here!Vol.1 has become Aoi, Ema, Shizuka, Misa and Midori!

name: SHIROBAKO vol.3
description: TV anime "SHIROBAKO" is to commemorate the fifth anniversary Infinite, it appeared in the LINE Sticker!
